    "To improve these limitations, it is recommended to further adjust the initial value distribution, optimize the exploration and utilization mechanism, and consider algorithm acceleration strategies in subsequent research in order to improve the stability and efficiency of the algorithm and better adapt to various complex optimization problems.",
    "This section evaluates how well BKA performed in resolving five elaborate engineering design issues: the design of a tension/compression spring, a pressure vessel, a welded beam, a speed reducer, and a three-bar truss design issue.",
    "These well-known engineering problems contain numerous equality and inequality constraints, and the ability of BKA to optimize real-world and constrained problems is evaluated from the perspective of constraint processing.",
    "Here, the constrained issues are transformed into unconstrained problems using a straightforward method of the death penalty.",
    "Solving constrained optimization problems is a crucial task in both optimization theory and applications."
